records.name: Raffles Maldives Meradhoo Resort

location.address: Raffles Maldives Meradhoo Meradhoo, Gaafu Alifu Atoll, Republic Of Maldives

descriptions.general: A total of 38 rooms are available for guests' convenience at Raffles Maldives Meradhoo Resort. There is Wi-Fi throughout the hotel. Those who stay at this establishment will appreciate the 24-hour reception. Raffles Maldives Meradhoo Resort does not offer cots on demand. This hotel is environmentally friendly. Transfer service is available for guests' convenience. In case of need, everyone staying at this accommodation may avail for health and wellness services. Raffles Maldives Meradhoo Resort may charge a fee for some services.
